erated in two highly tunable resonator modes. We verify wavelength tuning\nover 100 nm between both modes with a controllable bandwidth between 7.2 and 13\nMHz. Heralding of single photons yields anti-bunching with $g^{(2)}(0) < 0.2$.\nThis compact source provides unprecedented possibilities to couple to different\nphysical quantum systems and renders it ideal for the implementation of quantum\nrepeaters and optical quantum information processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 13 Apr 2012 17:21:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 22 Apr 2012 09:48:42 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 14 Nov 2012 02:58:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-24"}
