-edge mobiles are the bottleneck for network coverage and provide a\nplausible analytic framework for more realistic analysis of other multi-cell\ntechniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 14 Apr 2012 12:10:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 6 Dec 2012 09:17:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-07"}
